data.description: Don't miss out on this extraordinary opportunity to call this newly renovated gem your own. Whether you're a first-time buyer, downsizing, or seeking a savvy investment, this home has something special for you. Ideally situated just minutes away from schools, major highways, delectable dining, and the Mall of Stonecrest, this home welcomes you with its spacious, airy charm. Prepare to be dazzled by the expansive kitchen featuring luxurious quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, an abundance of storage space, and a seamless flow into the inviting fireside family room. From here, step out into the capacious backyard, where your dreams of adding a pool or an ADU (Accessory Dwelling Unit) for additional passive income can become a reality. Retreat to the generous primary bedroom, a sanctuary perfect for unwinding after a long day, or savor your morning coffee or evening wine outdoors on the front porch or backyard with serene views. At this enticing price point, this home is sure to steal your heart. Don't hesitate Co schedule a viewing today and witness its allure for yourself.
